706579f-a.title: Brooklyn: St. Johns Place - 8th Avenue
706579f-a.text:
St. John's Place, west from Eighth Ave., showing Grace Methodist
Episcopal Church at the right, and the Memorial Presbyterian Church at the
left, in the background.
August 2, 1928.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
